title: Mayor Papenfuse to Announce 2015 Harrisburg Holiday Parade on Monday (City of Harrisburg, PA)
text: ( Source : City of Harrisburg, PA ) MAYOR PAPENFUSE TO ANNOUNCE 2015 HARRISBURG HOLIDAY PARADE AT PRESS CONFERENCE MONDAY IN ATRIUM OF MLK GOVERNMENT CENTER SPONSORS WELCOME! Mayor Papenfuse will announce the theme and honorary Grand Marshals
